727434f-a.title: Queens: Metropolitan Avenue - 80th Street
727434f-a.text:
Metropolitan Ave., east of 80th Street (foreground,not seen).
St. John's Cemetery is shown at both sides of first mentioned Ave.
(fenced in). At the rioht is Fred Frey's hotel at the intersection of
Metropolitan and Cooper Ave.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
